OL,3,CFire Service needs to do more to keep
OL,4,Cpeople safe, report finds
OL,6,FA fire service must do more to improve
OL,7,Fhow it keeps people safe from fire and
OL,8,Fother rinks, inspectors have said.
OL,10,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,11,FConstabulary and Fire & Rescue
OL,12,FServices (HMICFRS) graded
OL,13,FGloucestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService's performance across 11 areas.
OL,16,FInspectors noted the service had
OL,17,Fimproved its communication with the
OL,18,Fpublic during emergency incidents, but
OL,19,Fsaid more work was needed.
