OL,3,CFire Service needs to do more to keep
OL,4,Cpeople safe, report finds
OL,6,FThe HMICFRS report rated the service
OL,7,Fas "adequate" in two areas, "requires
OL,8,Fimprovement" in six areas and
OL,9,F"inadequate" in three areas.
OL,11,FThe inspectorate said it has
OL,12,F"concerns" about Gloucestershire Fire
OL,13,Fand Rescue Service's ability to keep
OL,14,Fpeople safe.
OL,16,FIn particular, the report found the
OL,17,Fservice needs to do more to improve
OL,18,Fits process for inspecting buildings.
