OL,3,CFire Service needs to do more to keep
OL,4,Cpeople safe, report finds
OL,6,FInspectors said they were "concerned"
OL,7,Fthe service's departments don't always
OL,8,Fwork together well, adding they "saw
OL,9,Foccasions when the service was more
OL,10,Ffocused on trying to increase output
OL,11,Finstead of reducing the greatest risk
OL,12,Fto the public."
OL,14,FThe report also found not enough is
OL,15,Fbeing done to create a positive
OL,16,Fworkplace culture and promote the
OL,17,Fimportance of equality, diversity and
OL,18,Finclusion within the force.
