OL,3,CFire Service needs to do more to keep
OL,4,Cpeople safe, report finds
OL,6,FInspectors said they were
OL,7,F"disappointed" about the lack of
OL,8,Fprogress since the last inspection in
OL,9,F2021, but acknowledged that some
OL,10,Fimprovements had been made.
OL,12,F"The service should take encouragement
OL,13,Ffrom this as it continues to make
OL,14,Ffurther improvements," they added.
OL,16,FGloucestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,17,FService has been contacted for comment.
